headlines.description: — Meek Mill crashed a 76ers press conference and gave a shoutout to his favorite team. The rapper capped his impromptu remarks with “good win!”
headlines.shortLinkText: Embiid scores 26, leads 76ers past LeBron-less Lakers 105-87

events.name: Minnesota Timberwolves at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — Stephen Curry found his sweet shooting stroke again after a rough stretch and Klay Thompson kept the pressure on from the perimeter and with drives through the paint, healthy again at last.
headlines.shortLinkText: Curry, Thompson shoot Warriors past Wolves, 124-115
